    <briefdescription>
<para>A set of delete-file pointers deduplicated by delete-file identity. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Delete files, especially deletion vectors, are identified by location plus content offset and content size. This mirrors Java&apos;s <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1DeleteFileSet" kindref="compound">DeleteFileSet</ref> behavior. </para>
